---
title: 安裝執行 — phaseExecute 8 步
description: Listr2 任務序列：備份 → 設定 → 安裝 → 生成 → 打包 → 驗證
links:
  - config-protection: 配置保護策略
  - setup-main: 返回主流程
---
flowchart TD
    Start([phaseExecute 開始]) --> E1

    subgraph E1 ["[1/8] 完整備份 → dist/backup/"]
        direction LR
        B1["~/.claude/<br/>commands/ agents/ rules/<br/>hooks.json · settings.json<br/>keybindings.json"]
        B2["~/.zshrc<br/>~/.zshrc.local<br/>~/.ripgreprc"]
        B3["~/.zsh/modules/"]
    end

    E1 --> E2

    subgraph E2 ["[2/8] 全局配置 → ~/.claude/"]
        direction TB
        S1["settings.json<br/>smart merge<br/>只添加新 permissions<br/>不刪除用戶現有規則"]
        S1 --> S2["hooks/slack-dispatch.sh<br/>Slack 通知分發器<br/>僅 Slack feature 啟用時"]
    end

    E2 --> E3

    subgraph E3 ["[3/8] Claude 安裝 → ~/.claude/"]
        direction TB
        C1["runTarget: claude-dev"]
        C1 --> C2["commands/*.md<br/>manifest MD5 追蹤<br/>用戶修改過 → 跳過"]
        C1 --> C3["agents/*.md<br/>同上"]
        C1 --> C4["rules/*.md<br/>fixed:all 或 smartSelect"]
        C1 --> C5["hooks.json<br/>smart merge（保留用戶自訂 hook）"]
    end

    E3 --> E4

    subgraph E4 ["[4/8] ECC + Stacks（並行）"]
        direction LR
        EC1["ECC 外部資源<br/>fetchAllSources<br/>buildSyncResult<br/>writeSyncedFiles<br/>→ ~/.claude/"]
        EC2["技術棧 Stacks<br/>scan.mjs --init<br/>per-skill 規則生成"]
    end

    E4 --> E5

    subgraph E5 ["[5/8] CLAUDE.md → ~/.claude/projects/"]
        direction TB
        MD1["per-repo 迭代"]
        MD1 --> MD2{"repo.role?"}
        MD2 -->|"main"| MD3["AI 生成完整版<br/>技術棧 + 架構 + 規範 + 指令"]
        MD2 -->|"temp"| MD4["AI 生成精簡版<br/>快速上手 + 技術棧"]
        MD2 -->|"tool"| MD5["AI 生成最小版<br/>一句描述 + 使用方式"]
        MD3 --> MD6["deployProjectClaudeMd<br/>→ ~/.claude/projects/{encoded}/CLAUDE.md"]
        MD4 --> MD6
        MD5 --> MD6
    end

    E5 --> E6

    subgraph E6 ["[6/8] Plugin 打包 → dist/release/"]
        direction LR
        P1["ab-claude-dev.plugin<br/>(build-claude-dev-plugin.sh)"]
        P2["ab-slack-message.plugin<br/>(build-slack-plugin.sh)"]
    end

    E6 --> E7

    subgraph E7 ["[7/8] ZSH 模組 → ~/.zsh/modules/"]
        direction TB
        Z1["modules/*.zsh 部署<br/>diff 比較，無變更跳過"]
        Z1 --> Z2["~/.zshrc 部署<br/>個人設定自動遷移 → .zshrc.local"]
        Z2 --> Z3["~/.ripgreprc<br/>已有則跳過"]
    end

    E7 --> E8

    subgraph E8 ["[8/8] 驗證安裝完整性"]
        direction TB
        V1["檢查 commands/*.md"]
        V2["檢查 agents/*.md"]
        V3["檢查 rules/*.md"]
        V4["檢查 settings.json"]
        V5["檢查 hooks.json"]
        V6["檢查 CLAUDE.md x N repos"]
        V1 --> V7{"全部就位?"}
        V2 --> V7
        V3 --> V7
        V4 --> V7
        V5 --> V7
        V6 --> V7
        V7 -->|Yes| V8["N/N 就位"]
        V7 -->|No| V9["缺少 M 個 → Slack 警告"]
    end

    E8 --> End([phaseExecute 完成])

    click E1 "#config-protection"

    classDef backup fill:#8b5cf6,color:#fff,stroke:#8b5cf6
    classDef merge fill:#2ea043,color:#fff,stroke:#2ea043
    classDef ai fill:#d29922,color:#000,stroke:#d29922
    classDef verify fill:#1f6feb,color:#fff,stroke:#1f6feb

    class B1,B2,B3 backup
    class S1,C5 merge
    class MD2,MD3,MD4,MD5 ai
    class V1,V2,V3,V4,V5,V6,V7 verify
